sentence: As described in Financial Accounting Standards Board (FASB) Staff Position AAG INV-1 and SOP 94-4-1, Reporting of Fully Benefit Responsive Investment Contracts Held by Certain Investment Companies Subject to the AICPA Investment Company Guide and Defined-Contribution Health and Welfare and Pension Plans, which was codified in Accounting Standards Codification (ASC) 962-205-45, investment contracts held by a defined-contribution plan are required to be reported at fair value.
